      <title>英国北海石油游说团体警告暴利税增加将导致投资下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-north-sea-oil-lobby-warns-of-investment-slump-due-to-windfall-tax-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业游说团体警告称，英国针对北海石油和天然气的新税制可能导致投资下降 80% 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-north-sea-oil-lobby-warns-of-investment-slump-due-to-windfall-tax-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
